                 Drive Buck and his truck across the landscape 
                         from job to job, catching falling items to 
                      earn his Payload. Drive through Quarries, 
                Forests, Cities, and the Arctic Tundra (More 
               levels to come!).
             Catch as many items as you can, but beware of 
              items too big to catch. A two ton boulder 
                     could crush the truck.
               
         Complete levels and get paid. Miss too many                                          
        items and its game over.
             Catch items to increase the Payload. Catch 
       more than a few items in a row to multiply 
      your score and get medals.
